branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
The MIS is an effective addition to conveyors, vibratory feeders, magazines and hoppers for separating and feeding individual parts or work pieces on assembly and production lines. A floating mechanism separates the finger from the internal piston allowing for easier finger replacement.
&lt;/p&gt;

